.TH SP-SIM-APPRENTICESHIP 1 "Spherepop Tools" "1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
sp-sim-apprenticeship \- simulate apprenticeship pipeline fragility under automation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sp-sim-apprenticeship
.RB [ \-y " years" ]
.RB [ \-o " out.csv" ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
sp-sim-apprenticeship runs a local simulation illustrating a stylized dynamic:
short-term efficiency pressure plus automation growth reduces junior hiring,
which can later produce senior scarcity and organizational fragility.
.PP
This tool is synthetic and does not connect to real organizations or HR systems.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-y " years"
Years to simulate (default: 20).
.TP
.BI \-o " file"
Output CSV file (default: ./apprenticeship.csv).
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 on success, non-zero on error.
.SH SEE ALSO
sp-probe-goodhart(1), sp-drift-metrics(1)

